<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>Lost?</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Patrick+Hand&family=Nunito:wght@600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
body{
  margin:0;
  background:#fdf6e9;
  font-family:'Patrick Hand', cursive;
  color:#333;
}

.wrapper{
  max-width:700px;
  margin:40px auto;
  padding:20px;
}

.poster{
  background:#fffdf7;
  border:3px dashed #333;
  padding:20px;
  box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
  transform:rotate(-1deg);
}

h1{
  text-align:center;
  font-size:42px;
  margin:0;
}

.sub{
  text-align:center;
  font-size:20px;
  margin:5px 0 15px;
}

.photo{
  text-align:center;
  margin:15px 0;
}

.photo img{
  width:280px;
  border:8px solid white;
  box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
  transform:rotate(2deg);
}

.section{
  font-size:22px;
  line-height:1.6;
  margin-top:10px;
}

ul{
  margin-top:5px;
}

.bottom{
  margin-top:25px;
  border-top:2px dashed #333;
  padding-top:15px;
  font-size:22px;
}

.tabs{
  margin-top:20px;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  font-size:16px;
}

.tab{
  border:1px dashed #333;
  padding:8px 12px;
  margin-top:10px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="poster">

    <h1>HAVE YOU SEEN THIS WOMAN?</h1>
    <div class="sub">Last seen being adorable and slightly grumpy.</div>

    <div class="photo">
      <img src="angel.jpg" alt="Angel">
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <strong>Description:</strong>
      <ul>
        <li>Excellent mom</li>
        <li>Excellent cook</li>
        <li>Kind, steady, and warm</li>
        <li>Loves mushrooms, water, and nature</li>
        <li>Sexy as f</li>
        <li>Yes, again — sexy as f</li>
        <li>The epitome of feminine glory</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="bottom">
      She’s not lost.  
      I just wanted everyone to know how awesome my girlfriend is.
      <br><br>
      If found: you can f right off.  
      <br><br>
      She’s my woman.
    </div>

    <div class="tabs">
      <div class="tab">Sexy as f</div>
      <div class="tab">Mine</div>
      <div class="tab">Grumpy Angel</div>
      <div class="tab">Taken</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
